tedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3504444" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Markus Spiske，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>由于违反 GDPR 的罚款可能高达数百万美元，理论上该公司更愿意支付据称更便宜的赎金。</p><p>索尼就此事接受了<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/sony-launches-investigation-after-ransomware-group-claims-to-have-breached-companys-systems"><em>IGN</em></a>采访，表示“目前正在调查此事”，并且“目前没有进一步评论”。然而，Ransomed.vc 已表示将于 9 月 28 日发布其非法来源的数据。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-3"><em>《收获日 3》</em></a>的开发商正在“考虑” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-looking-at-an-offline-mode-following-disastrous-launch-3504342">删除游戏始终在线功能的想法，因为该游戏</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox 系列</a>上推出时都遇到了技术问题。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-is-investigating-claims-that-all-of-its-systems-have-been-hacked-3504374">索尼正在“调查”声称其“所有”系统都遭到黑客攻击的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
